"Software" refers to the Smart Attendance System, including but not limited to:
  - Source code (app.py, templates, static files, JavaScript, CSS)
  - Database schemas and structure (schema.sql, SQLite databases)
  - Face recognition models and algorithms (Haar Cascade, KNN classifier)
  - Documentation (README.md, PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md)
